   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-2" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300325">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-3" mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, here you are.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>You brought <FONT color=#a82424>Fire Elf's Powder</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-3" image="QN_Npc_Saint_BlackSmith_Dwarf.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-3-a" mid="86"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="85"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Hmm, it's definitely Fire Elf's Powder!<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Berlin puts Fire Elf's Powder into the kiln. It bursts into burning flames.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-3-a" image="QN_Npc_Saint_BlackSmith_Dwarf.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-3-b" mid="88"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="87"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>The flame's become very strong.<BR>
That's all we need to get remnants melted<FONT color=#7e12d2> </FONT> and pour this into hammer mold.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Berlin puts the weapon remnants into the mold.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-3-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-3-c" mid="90"><![CDATA[<html>That's why you sent me to run the errand.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="89"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>What's important in this process is to keep the firepower big enough to melt the Epic loots. The firepower was getting weaker, but thanks to Fire Elf's Powder you brought, the flames are much stronger now.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-3-c" image="QN_Npc_Saint_BlackSmith_Dwarf.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-3-d" mid="92"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="91"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Well, not really. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Berlin seems to feel a prick of conscience.)</FONT><BR>Anyway,<BR>
we don't return broken weapons to the clients because we recycle all.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-3-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-3-e" mid="94"><![CDATA[<html>(What should I tell…)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="93"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>So, the rumor of us siphoning off weapons are all untrue.<BR>
I want you to let people know about this.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
