   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-3-f" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-3-g" mid="100"><![CDATA[<html>(………)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="97"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>What do you think? Broken weapons are recycled in an eco-friendly manner. I don't break weapons with the purpose of a new hammer… ah… ahchoo…!<BR>
It's dusty here, suddenly… hmm….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
